          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8012423">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8012423/" class="title-link">回忆战争是为了再无战争</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8012423"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/48051798/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u48051798-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48051798/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">沈一默</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-07-28"
      class="main-meta">2016-07-28 23:06:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8012423_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  伴随着曾经看过的美国电影，拯救大兵瑞恩和许多的国产抗日剧的回忆，我开始了浴血太平洋的阅读。不同于小说的虚构改编，这本书是回忆录，一切都是曾经真实发生过的。读来虽然不像小说那样跌宕起伏，但是它的真实更能触动人们的心灵。 战争总是残酷的，在老兵吉姆.麦克埃内的回...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
